### Create Client
POST http://localhost:8080/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "description": "High net worth individual interested in tech stocks and real estate.",
  "social_links": [
    {
      "platform": "LinkedIn",
      "url": "https://linkedin.com/in/johndoe"
    }
  ]
}

> {%
  client.global.set("clientId", response.body.id);
%}

###

### Get Client
GET http://localhost:8080/clients/{{clientId}}

###

### Create Document for Client
POST http://localhost:8080/clients/{{clientId}}/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Investment Strategy 2025",
  "content": "The client prefers long-term growth investments with a moderate risk tolerance. Focus on diversified portfolio including S&P 500 index funds, government bonds, and selected tech equities. Avoid speculative assets and cryptocurrencies."
}

> {%
  client.global.set("documentId", response.body.id);
%}

###

### Get Client Document
GET http://localhost:8080/clients/{{clientId}}/documents/{{documentId}}

###
